        },
        {
          "text": "User Story:",
          "bold": true
        },
        {
          "text": " As a humanities student, I want to annotate audio recordings so that I can present my close listening work as an assignment. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Description:",
          "bold": true
        },
        {
          "text": " Annotations can be added to an audio recording to capture and communicate the insights and analysis generated by close listening to the recording. Relevant fields include English, Social Studies, Film Studies, and Music and Sound Studies. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Ingredients:",
          "bold": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "numbered-list",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "list-item",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "1 or more audio recordings"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list-item",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Annotations"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list-item",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Tags (optional) "
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Method:",
          "bold": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "numbered-list",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "list-item",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Perform close listening of audio recording(s), making note of observations and analyses with timestamps for all notes"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list-item",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Upload audio recording(s) to AVAnnotate and add annotations, following "
            },
            {
              "type": "link",
              "url": "https://av-annotate.org/how-to-use/",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Quick Start: How to use AVAnnotate"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": " guide"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list-item",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Create and add tags to annotations, if desired, following Quick Start guide "
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
